name: STARMASK (WALLET)
description:
This is our **Crypto Wallet**. Available for **multiplatforms**, this application aims to revolutionize the way we use **crypto assets**. **Maximum supply is limited in the contract to 300,000**. The app will be **public and free**, but **NFT holders** will be able to **unlock exclusive perks**.

It is in the development process and the whitelist is not defined yet.
